*   ## **_BLOODLINE RULES WWE CHAMPIONSHIP: CODY RHODES (C) DEF. SOLO SIKOA_**
    

Decent match. The Bloodline interferemce is thwarted by Kevin Owens and Randy Orton.

Until Jacob Fatu comes out and puts Cody through the announce table, potentially injuring his own leg in the process

This should allow Solo to win the title but…

ROMAN REIGNS HELPS CODY RHODES RETAIN THE WWE CHAMPIONSHIP

WHAT A FINAL STRETCH!! WHAT A GREAT STORY FOCUSED PAY PER VIEW!!

